title: FC Krasnogvardeyets Moscow
text: FC Krasnogvardeyets Moscow () was a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> team from <a href="Moscow">Moscow</a>. It played professionally from 1995 to 1997. Their best result was 14th place in Zone 3 of the <a href="Russian%20Third%20League">Russian Third League</a> in 1996 and 1997.
